4.2 alignat
\begin{alignat}{2}
 \sigma_1 &= x + y  &\quad \sigma_2 &= \frac{x}{y} \\   
 \sigma_1' &= \frac{\partial x + y}{\partial x} & \sigma_2' 
    &= \frac{\partial \frac{x}{y}}{\partial x}
\end{alignat}
